videos.description: Luke Falk passes to Tavares Martin Jr. for a 21- yard touchdown to put the Cougars on the board.
videos.headline: Cougars score early with a Martin Jr. TD

videos.description: Luke Falk passes to Jamal Morrow but gets sacked in the end zone by Oregon State's Shawn Wilson resulting in a safety.
videos.headline: Oregon State sacks in the end zone for a safety

videos.description: Luke Falk connects with Isaiah Johnson-Mack for an impressive 20-yard catch resulting in a Washington touchdown.
videos.headline: Cougars increase lead with an impressive TD catch

videos.description: Ryan Nall runs for 7-yards for a touchdown to chip away at Washington's lead.
videos.headline: Oregon State gets on the board with first TD of the game

videos.description: Isaiah Johnson-Mack makes a diving 26-yard catch to get the Cougars into the red zone.
videos.headline: Johnson-Mack makes great diving catch for Washington State

videos.description: Luke Falk and Tavares Martin Jr. connect once again for 2-yard touchdown adding to the Cougars lead.
videos.headline: Washington State cushions lead with  Martin Jr. TD

videos.description: Punter Nick Porebski fumbles the ball and is recovered by Cougar's Gerard Wicks for first down .
videos.headline: Punt attempt results in costly fumble for Oregon State

videos.description: Luke Falk passes to Isaiah Johnson-Mack for their second touchdown of the game increasing Washington State's lead.
videos.headline: Cougars's Luke Falk is on a roll with another TD

videos.description: Beavers black the field goal and recover the ball.
videos.headline: Oregon State blocks Washington State's FG attempt

videos.description: Ryan Nall breaks several tackles and runs an impressive 45-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Beavers run their way into the end zone

videos.description: Cougar's Tavares Martin Jr. catches deep pass from Luke Falk and runs it 57-yards for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Washington State QB Falk goes deep for TD

videos.description: Luke Falk connects with Kyle Sweet for a 10- yard touchdown for Washington State.
videos.headline: Cougars' Sweet hustles his way into the end zone

videos.description: Beavers QB Jake Luton gets sacked by Washington State's Marcellus Pippins and the fumble is picked up by Frankie Luvu who takes it back for a score.
videos.headline: Oregon State has costly fumble

videos.description: Luke Falk throws for 396 yards and six scores in No. 21 Washington State's 52-23 win over Oregon State. Beavers QB Jake Luton was carted off the field in the fourth quarter with an injury, but gave a thumbs up as he left the field.
videos.headline: Falk leads Washington State to rout Oregon State
